videos.description: Neil O'Connor starts the scoring from 10 yards out to put the Wildcats in the lead.
videos.headline: O'Connor TD reception puts New Hampshire on the board first

videos.description: Trevor Knight breaks off a big gain in the open field for New Hampshire.
videos.headline: Knight shows off speed outside of pocket

videos.description: Georgia Southern safety Jay Bowdry goes to make a tackle and does not get up. Bowdry would be carted off the field.
videos.headline: Bowdry put in stretcher and carted off the field

videos.description: L.A. Ramsby cuts the deficit in half for Georgia Southern.
videos.headline: Ramsby punches it in for the Eagles first TD
